&lt;p&gt;Trackonomy is seeking dependable and detail-oriented Production Operators to support second shift manufacturing operations at our North Carolina facility. Operators will be responsible for producing RFID labels and smart tracking products while maintaining high standards for safety, quality, productivity, and accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for individuals who enjoy hands-on work, can follow detailed processes, and take pride in producing high-quality products in a team-oriented manufacturing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
