&lt;li&gt;Load materials, monitor production runs, and perform basic equipment adjustments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately complete production documentation and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, organized, and safe work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support inventory movement and material handling as needed&lt;/li&gt;
